Usage: get_ptn_fplan_mode [-help] [-export] [-import] [-quiet] [-nonDefault]

-help       # Prints out the command usage
-export    # Export setting
           # (enums={macro special_route pin_constraint}_list, default=special_route)
-import    # Import setting
           # (enums={macro special_route pin_constraint}_list, default="")
-quiet      # Displays the current settings in Tcl list format only
-nonDefault # Displays the current settings which are not default settings